menu "Gas Meter Configuration"

    config REED_SENSOR_GPIO
        int "Reed sensor GPIO pin"
        default 7
        help
            GPIO pin connected to the reed sensor of the gas meter.
            The pin is configured with an internal pull-up; the reed
            switch should pull it to ground when closed.

    config IDENTIFY_LED_GPIO
        int "Identification LED GPIO pin"
        default 15
        help
            GPIO pin connected to the onboard LED used for
            Matter Identify cluster visual feedback.

endmenu
